                    <description>&lt;p&gt;On the web page of the maven-surefire-plugin i have found that the description for the include rules of the &lt;a href=&quot;http://maven.apache.org/surefire/maven-surefire-plugin/test-mojo.html#includes&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;maven-surefire-plugin&lt;/a&gt; shows the description of the maven-failsafe-plugin.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
